  Technical Details:

  In Pydantic v2, field constraints are not stored as direct attributes on FieldInfo. Instead, they are stored as separate constraint objects in the metadata list. The code must:
  1. Iterate through the metadata list
  2. Use isinstance() checks with constraint protocols to identify constraint types
  3. Extract values from the matched constraint objects

